    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he told us he's gonna go home and bring us food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think my parents almost died because the night before, my mother came there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the meantime, when I-- In the meantime, my uncle Chaim was there also.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So there was my father, and my brother, Uncle Chaim and my mother, and myself on Christmas-- on the Russian Christmas Day when he found us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he says, I'm gonna go home and bring you some hot food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think they would have rather been in Siberia then wait for him with the food, because they thought this is the last day of our life.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
